comments: LLB shows Huerter (ATL) extends his arm in front of Burks (NYK), however, the offensive player brings their arm up and around Huerter's arm and holds the hook as the two players move towards the ball.
Burks (NYK) and Hunter (ATL) engage and disengage after the pick is set by Hunter.
During the post shot attempt, Barrett (NYK) raises his arms into the vertical arm of Hunter (ATL) and arm contact occurs that is simultaneous to Hunter's contact with the ball.
RAR shows Bogdanovic (ATL) reaches in with his right hand and makes direct contact with the ball to deflect it away from Barrett (NYK).
Hunter (ATL) moves laterally along Barrett's (NYK) path and some marginal contact occurs that has no impact on the latter's SQBR.
Hunter (ATL) and Quickley (NYK) engage and disengage after the pick.
Robinson (NYK) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Young (ATL), who adjusts his posture to avoid the screen.
Bogdanovic (ATL) briefly grazes the left arm of Quickley (NYK) after the gather and the marginal touch has no impact on the driving shot attempt.
Capela (ATL) touches the ball after it makes contact with the backboard and has a chance to score.
During the inbound play, Robinson (NYK) extends his left arm into the path of Hunter (ATL) and removes it shortly thereafter and the contact is marginal.
Burks (NYK) reaches around Young (ATL) and commits a take foul.
Burks (NYK) commits a take foul on Huerter (ATL).
Bogdanovic (ATL) places and removes a hand from the side of Quickley (NYK) after his gather and the marginal touch has no impact on the driving shot attempt.
Gibson (NYK) reaches across the front of Young (ATL) and makes contact with his body that alters the Young's SQBR.
Capela (ATL) swings his arms down but does not make any contact with Barrett (NYK).
Hunter (ATL) reaches in and makes marginal contact with the left arm of Burks (NYK) that does not impact the latter's dribble.
